Packages 
Package Description
uniandes.unacloud.common.com
In this package are located all classes used to create udp communication message for Unacloud
uniandes.unacloud.common.com.messages
In this package are located all classes which represents main messages and responses for TCP communication between control and agent programs.
uniandes.unacloud.common.com.messages.agent
In this package are located all classes which represents request sent from server to process task in agent
uniandes.unacloud.common.com.messages.exeo
In this package are located all classes which represents request sent from server to process task in executions
uniandes.unacloud.common.com.messages.pmo
In this package are located all classes which represents request sent from server to process task in physical machine
uniandes.unacloud.common.com.messages.udp  
uniandes.unacloud.common.enums
In this package are located all enum used by agent and server projects
uniandes.unacloud.common.utils
In this package are located all utility classes to execute commands in terminal, generate tokens and random numbers, request environment variables, and other operations used to configure executions and communication with server.
